<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>س ل ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٥٨٠ - س ل ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سِلْف/ سَلِف <span class="c4">[مفرد]</span>: ج أَسْلاف، مؤ سِلْفة/ سَلِفة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• سِلْف الرَّجُل:</span> عديلُه؛ زوج أخت امرأته.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• سِلْف المرأة:</span> شقيقُ زوجِها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• السِّلفان:</span> العديلان.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>